WEBVTT

00:02.584 --> 00:05.387
The farm animals were standing on a hill.

00:06.361 --> 00:07.351
Goat said.

00:07.872 --> 00:10.819
Look at that little barn on the other hill.

00:11.472 --> 00:13.868
I think I will go to the barn.

00:14.825 --> 00:15.657
said Goat.

00:16.715 --> 00:20.101
Goat ran down the hill and across a field.

00:21.049 --> 00:24.680
Oh no, Goat is shrinking.

00:25.839 --> 00:26.775
said Cow.

00:27.781 --> 00:29.341
Goat ran farther.

00:30.400 --> 00:33.407
Goodness me, Goat is shrinking more.

00:34.522 --> 00:35.544
said Cow.

00:36.403 --> 00:38.715
Goat ran even farther.

00:39.529 --> 00:43.043
Oh no, now Goat has disappeared.

00:43.956 --> 00:44.954
said Cow.

00:46.213 --> 00:49.489
I will fly to the barn to find Goat.

00:50.405 --> 00:51.340
said Duck.

00:52.347 --> 00:54.839
Duck began to fly to the barn.

00:56.010 --> 00:59.380
Oh no, Duck is shrinking, too.

01:00.201 --> 01:01.239
said Cow.

01:02.102 --> 01:03.691
Duck flew farther.

01:04.728 --> 01:08.244
Oh no, now Duck has disappeared.

01:09.301 --> 01:10.178
said Cow.

01:11.181 --> 01:14.379
I will run to the barn and find Goat and Duck.

01:15.082 --> 01:15.963
said Pig.

01:16.958 --> 01:18.837
Pig ran to the barn.

01:19.913 --> 01:23.038
Oh no, Pig is shrinking, too.

01:24.341 --> 01:25.303
said Cow.

01:26.324 --> 01:28.747
Pig ran farther and farther.

01:29.675 --> 01:33.226
Goodness me, now Pig has disappeared.

01:34.249 --> 01:35.243
said Cow.

01:36.147 --> 01:39.414
I'd better go find Pig, Duck, and Goat.

01:40.237 --> 01:41.211
she said.

01:42.049 --> 01:45.001
Cow began to run toward the barn.

01:45.870 --> 01:47.493
She ran down the hill.

01:48.592 --> 01:50.964
The barn began to get bigger.

01:52.038 --> 01:54.069
Cow ran across the field.

01:55.024 --> 01:57.891
The barn became bigger and bigger.

01:59.025 --> 02:00.657
Cow reached the barn.

02:01.680 --> 02:04.907
She could see it was a very big barn.

02:05.898 --> 02:08.564
She saw Pig, Duck, and Goat.

02:09.652 --> 02:11.514
They had not disappeared!

